Once apon a time there was a man who lived in a forest.
This man had a lion who would go hunting everyday to bring him food.
one day the lion went hunting but he didn't come home,so the man went looking for him.
he then found out that his lion was kidnapped by a witch.
the man snuck into the witch's house and freed his lion when she wasn't looking.
the lion ate the witch and then the man and his lion went home.
